This,lightweight,API,is,used,within,Google,and,made,available,to,other,developers,It,makes,all,of,Google,s,APIs,listable,and,provides,additional,information,about,each,API,including,a,full,list,of,resources,or,methods,Google,uses,the,API,Discovery,API,internally,to,maintain,client,libraries,for,all,of,its,APIs,as,well,as,to,fill,a,sandbox,with,potential,API,calls